  1    0    1    1    0    B2   B1   B0   Left Channel, -10dB/step
  0    0    1    0    A3   A2   A1   A0   Right Channel, -1dB/step
  0    0    1    1    0    B2   B1   B0   Right Channel, -10dB/step
